Akken daɣen i ččan tamanna deg unezṛuf, i gteddun am izgaren, ulli ur nesɛi ara taftilt iwakken a ț-nɣumm s tili n tḥellel.
Tameddit n wass i deg țheggin iman-nsen i wass n westeɛfu, daymi a luḍu ; lɛaddat-agi llant-ed d lemtel kan armi d asmi yerra Sidi Ṛebbi kullec d ajdid.
Ayen akk s ɣuṛ Ṛebbi i d-tekka yerna tlemdeḍ s ɣuṛ Sidi Ṛebbi ; ma d kečč, ula d kečč aț-țețmeslayeḍ-ed fell-ak, ayen i gețnuzun seg yimi-s, sɛut akk-d imeqqranen n tejmaɛt.
?ef wayen yeɛnan izuṛan n lejdud akk-d igelliden n ddunit, ayagi meṛṛa d ayen i gețmeslayen.
Taqsiṭ-agi tesɛa lmeɛna nniḍen : « ț-țagi i d nennekmal » meɛna ilaq a d-yedṛu wayen yuran di tira iqedsen : ayen ara sen-d-ssukksen, ilaq a t- nexdem iwakken ad yedṛu wayen yuran di tira iqedsen.
Awal-agi d awal n tideț yuklalen ad ițwafehmen di tmurt n Selyan imi aṭas i t-id-ițxebbiṛen s ɣuṛ Sidi Ṛebbi.
Eɛni ilaq a d-yas kra n wayen yellan di tebṛaț-agi s ɣuṛ Baba Ṛebbi ? Neɣ m'ara ṛuḥen ad awin tabṛaț-nni i yi-d-ițțasen s ɣuṛ Sidi Ṛebbi iwakken a sen-sǧehden ayen akk i wen-d-nnan lmuqedmin ;
Ini daɣen i temɣarin ad sɛunt tikli yeṣfan, ur ilaq ara ad ilint ț-țiqeṛṛaḍin, ur ilaq ara ad țḥawalent tissit n ccṛab meɛna ilaq ad nehhunt ɣer wayen eɛzizen.
Iles daɣen ț-țimes, d bab n lbaṭel, yesɛa amkan di lǧețța-s yerna yessamas akk taṛwiḥt-agi, yesseṛɣay akk tudert-nsen.
Imi d-tesbeggnem belli tqeddcem ɣef ṭṭhaṛa-nni i sɛan di lɛadda-nsen, ilaq ad ṛuḥen ad slemden s waṭas yimeslayen yemxalafen ; ilaq a sen-t-id-ɛiwdeɣ s ɣuṛ-wen :
Meɛna ma yella acḥal teḍyeḍ, acḥal yewɛeṛ : yewɛeṛ ɣer zdat ur k-yețțak ara awal iwakken aț-țesfehmeḍ timeslayin-agi n lxiṛ.
Asmi lliɣ ḍefṛen watmaten n temdint n Ispanya. Tețwajeb daɣen ilaq a d-aɣen s ɣuṛ-es imi ur tezmirem ara a t-txedmem, zemren ad țewten s ujelkkaḍ ( s lexbaṛ ).
Aṭas seg wat Isṛail i gɛuṣan Sidi Ṛebbi yerna țkellixen medden s imeslayen-nsen,
M'ara d-yaweḍ lweqt n twaɣit ara yedṛun di zzman n tmeddit, iban-ed ɛinani zdat lɣaci, yerna aṭas n wid ara yilin di temdint ama di tmurt-agi, yerna ad țțafen deg-s izedganen.
Akken daɣen, aṭas n wid yesselmaden lekdeb i d-ikkan si lǧedra-nsen.
Aț-țili d leǧwahi n tnac n wass wis tmanya, kkiɣ-ed si ccetlat n temdint n Kurintus, yuɣal d aɛessas n temdint n Jafa.
Ajṛad-nni yecba iɛewdiwen iheggan i umenɣi, sɛan ɣef yiqeṛṛay nsen am akken ț-țiɛeṣṣabin n ቻይn.
Di temdint n Jafa, leǧwahi n tejmaɛt n Arimati akk-d wid n temdint n Yiriku heggan iman-nsen d agellid, xedmen ccɣel-nsen ; wid yumnen s Lmasiḥ, d atmaten kan i gextaṛ Sidi Ṛebbi.
M'ara ț-țerren ɣer wakal tețțuɣal d ulac, meɛna m'ara d-teḥyu, a d-teḥyu s ṣṣifa n wemdan iwakken a ț-țerren ɣer wakal teffeɣ-iț tezmert, m'ara d-teḥyu a d-teḥyu s lǧehd d ameqqran.
Nețwaḥṛes si mkul tama meɛna ur nefcil ara ; nella di teswiɛt n ṭṭiq akk-d yir tikli i wen-d-yusan s ɣuṛ Ṛebbi, ur yețțili ara deg-wen s tḥila,
Di lweqt-nni kan, Ilaq-aɣ a nḍuɛ imdebbṛen n lḥukuma, yețțawi-t yerna ad yefk tazmert s wayes ara nnernin di liman. Ihi m'ara iṛuḥ a d-yawi lexbaṛ n lxiṛ ɣef wayen ara s-d-yawi ɣer wanda yebɣa.
Ma yella yewweḍ-ed leḥcic yellan di tegniț n north, Ikaddab-nni baba-tneɣ Akadar, illan ț-țilawin-nsen deɛwessu n ddunit ameqqran, ilaq aț-țnehhuḍṣeḍ iwakken aț-țețẓuḍem s wezṛuḥ.
Tamdint-agi, țmettilen-d imekkasen n tebzert ( leɣṛama ) ɣer lɣeṛba ; wid i gextaṛ Sidi Ṛebbi a ten-yeǧǧa di beṛṛa n taddart n Arimati, llan gar-asen Isḥaq, Yeɛqub akk-d wid yellan yid-sen.
M'ara ɛeṛdeḍ, awi-d yid-ek abeṛnus-nni i ǧǧiḍ deg wexxam n Karbus di tmurt n Arimati n wasif n Urdun, isselmad asen ayen ur nețbecciṛ ara, aț-țessiweḍ lexbaṛ n lxiṛ,
Yella yiwen yeqqaṛ llan wussan yesɛan azal akteṛ n wiyaḍ, ma ɣer wayeḍ ussan akk ɛedlen ur mxalafen ara. Mkul yiwen ilaq ad itḥeqqeq deg wayen ițxemmim.
Akken daɣen i tedṛa d imezdaɣ n temdinin n Luri, cedda ț-țizegzawin n temdinin n Gumuṛ, ikeṛṛuṛen ɣlayen n temdint n Rinya, deg mkul ṣṣenf akk-d ddheb,
Ilaq-awen aț-țɛiwneḍ tijeḥnaḍ ț-țsuqas am tid n tɣerdmiwin ; di tjeḥnaḍ-agi i tella tezmert n tideț.
Mkul Tafaska n izimer n leslak Bilaṭus yețserriḥ-ed i yiwen umeḥbus. Mkul Tafaska n izimer n leslak tqeṛb-ed seg wass amezwaru.
Si zik aṭas n wid yumnen s Lmasiḥ, i gellan di tejmaɛt n imasiḥiyen akk-d wid ur nelli ara n wat Isṛail, i gextaṛ Sidi Ṛebbi, d wid ur nețțak ara s Lmasiḥ ad sɛun leqdeṛ.
Awal-agi d awal n Baba Ṛebbi yețțili deg-s wayen ara s-d-ssukksen, mbla tamtunt ( iɣes ) iwakken s ɣuṛ Ṛebbi ur d-yekkat ara deg yiḍ n lɛid n Izimer n leslak.
Lemfaṣel-agi i d-yețbanen d imecṭaḥ, nefɛen aṭas seg wat Isṛail, d wid i gextaṛ Sidi Ṛebbi iwumi i d-yessawel Sidi Ṛebbi.
Aṭas n tajmaɛt n imasiḥiyen i gellan di tejmaɛt n imasiḥiyen mkul amkan alamma ț-țaggara, i d-yed terbaɛt n Ssid-nneɣ Ɛisa Lmasiḥ, i gellan d igellilen. Mmugren-d deg yiḍ n lɛid n Izimer ara d-yasen si tejmaɛt n watmaten, am akken i d-tenna ccariɛa n Sidna Ɛisa Lmasiḥ.
Amdan yezmer ad iḥeṛṛeb yal ṣṣenf n lewḥuc : ama d wid iteddun ɣef ṛebɛa iḍaṛṛen, ama d ifṛax, ama d izerman ama d lewḥuc n lebḥeṛ yerna ț-țideț iɣleb-iten meṛṛa.
Seg wasmi i d-texleq ddunit werǧin nesli s yiwen yeldi-d tiflukin iwakken ur yezmir ara a d-isbeggen iman-is di lewqat n ddheb. Daymi i t-ițnawi talalit n ddheb, ilaq ad yili d aɛeryan.
M'ara d-yaweḍ wass i deg ara nsel i ubeḥri tiɛiqeṛt-nni, ilaq a d-aɣen ayen akk ara ččen.
M'ara d-taseḍ, awi-d yid-ek abeṛnus-nni i ǧǧiɣ deg wexxam n Karbus di leɛḍim, neɣ m'ulac a d-yawi yiḍ di ddunit. M'ara yura di tira iqedsen : Ili yiṭij n ddunit, ur d-yekki ara seg umkan-is.
Tikkelt tis snat, ṣṣut-nni i d-yekkan seg igenni wezger-ines tgerger iman-is, tețfeǧǧiǧ akteṛ n wass,
D ugur ameqqran m'ara ṭṭfen imukan gar-awen ɣer imensi n tegmaț, zehhun mbla lḥecma, țxemmimen kan ɣef yiman-nwen ; cban ttjuṛ ur d-nețțak ara lqima n wayen akk yesɛa.
Ini i yemɣaṛen ad setqenɛen, ad fken leqdeṛ i yiman-nsen, ad sɛun leɛqel, ad amnen s Sidi Ṛebbi.
Ajṛad-nni yecba iɛewdiwen iheggan i umenɣi, sɛan ɣef yiqeṛṛay nsen am akken ț-țiɛeṣṣabin n wid ițbeddilen idrimen, a sen-yefk ad xedmen i wid yeznuzun itbiren.
iwakken ad isseɣli lqima n yisem n Sidi Ṛebbi, ad rren ddehn-nneɣ ɣer tmucuha.
Lqebṭan n lǧameɛ d wid i gemɣalen-t-id snitrat i wid i gextaṛ Sidi Ṛebbi, yețțak-asen tazmert s wayes ara neqdec irren awal-nsen.
